data.description: MLS# 20376916 - Built by Trophy Signature Homes - Ready Now! ~ Perennially popular, the Primary boasts everything you could want in a home and more. Offering even more space, the five-bedroom design is sure to be the go-to home for holiday dinners with a open living room large enough to provide for abundant seating. The island kitchen is equipped for cooking in full swing, turning out everything from canapes to a turkey with all the trimmings. Boasting game and media rooms, the upstairs is an entertainer’s paradise. If you don’t need all five bedrooms, it’s easy to turn one or two into a home office, playroom or den!
